she illegally crossed into Cambodia

58
00:11:05,304 --> 00:11:06,731
and entered an underground casino.

59
00:11:07,971 --> 00:11:08,932
How can we investigate?

60
00:11:10,091 --> 00:11:12,811
Wait. Why can't we investigate then?

61
00:11:13,691 --> 00:11:16,052
We'll just go to Cambodia.

62
00:11:16,532 --> 00:11:17,532
Will you fund the trip?

63
00:11:17,851 --> 00:11:18,731
Will you go?

64
00:11:18,932 --> 00:11:19,971
Then go now.

65
00:11:21,211 --> 00:11:24,172
I could find an agent to go to Cambodia.

66
00:11:27,532 --> 00:11:29,211
Listen. Check it.

67
00:11:29,491 --> 00:11:34,132
Check if there's any proof that Ren Xiaoming
returned to Qidaohezi in August 2010

68
00:11:34,451 --> 00:11:36,892
and visited Rest Cemetery.

69
00:11:37,611 --> 00:11:39,012
Before August.

70
00:11:39,292 --> 00:11:42,571
Also, there's another key person.

71
00:11:44,652 --> 00:11:45,451
Bai Shu.

72
00:11:46,372 --> 00:11:49,211
According to the plot
in the chapter, Leopard and Graveyard,

73
00:11:49,412 --> 00:11:51,091
she should be at the crime scene too.

74
00:11:51,611 --> 00:11:54,252
She seems to have always hoped
we'd uncover the truth.

75
00:11:54,731 --> 00:11:57,932
If she knew
Ren Xiaoming was the murderer,

76
00:11:58,252 --> 00:12:00,252
why wouldn't she tell us directly?

77
00:12:04,211 --> 00:12:07,532
Telling you directly
might not leave a deep impression.

78
00:12:19,571 --> 00:12:20,172
You're here.

79
00:12:20,971 --> 00:12:22,172
What can I do for you?

80
00:12:24,012 --> 00:12:28,571
I can prove Ren Xiaoming was
in Qidaohezi in August 2010.

81
00:12:31,811 --> 00:12:32,851
Are you sure?

82
00:12:34,052 --> 00:12:34,892
I'm sure.

83
00:12:35,491 --> 00:12:39,012
Because Wang Hao came to see me
the day before Ren Xiaoming returned.

84
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:44,818
