85
00:12:48,292 --> 00:12:48,851
Shu.

86
00:12:51,932 --> 00:12:52,491
Shu.

87
00:12:53,811 --> 00:12:57,012
I know you don't want to see me
or hear my explanation.

88
00:12:57,451 --> 00:12:59,491
But I think I must tell you the truth.

89
00:12:59,892 --> 00:13:03,731
That day in Wuchuan,
I didn't do anything bad to you.

90
00:13:03,971 --> 00:13:04,611
I know.

91
00:13:05,731 --> 00:13:06,412
You know?

92
00:13:07,412 --> 00:13:08,412
Why didn't you expose it?

93
00:13:08,971 --> 00:13:12,052
You'd say nothing to protect Ge Wenjun.

94
00:13:13,532 --> 00:13:15,292
When the police
told me the test results,

95
00:13:16,132 --> 00:13:17,451
I guessed what had happened.

96
00:13:19,091 --> 00:13:22,172
I also guessed you came to me
because you're leaving.

97
00:13:22,731 --> 00:13:23,851
With no plan to return.

98
00:13:25,731 --> 00:13:26,331
Exactly.

99
00:13:26,772 --> 00:13:29,292
I'm going abroad. I won't come back.

100
00:13:30,412 --> 00:13:32,172
So you came here to tell me the truth

101
00:13:32,532 --> 00:13:34,731
because you don't want to leave,
burdened with guilt.

102
00:13:37,331 --> 00:13:38,412
You're quite selfish.

103
00:13:39,691 --> 00:13:43,172
Shu, I just don't want you
to find this world so repulsive.

104
00:13:44,012 --> 00:13:46,611
If you really don't want me
to find this world so repulsive,

105
00:13:47,412 --> 00:13:50,851
