189
00:21:37,172 --> 00:21:38,572
Long time, Mr. He.

190
00:21:38,771 --> 00:21:40,092
I know you're laughing at me.

191
00:21:40,332 --> 00:21:41,051
How's business?

192
00:21:41,251 --> 00:21:43,332
Pretty good.
I just sold a pair of pants.

193
00:21:43,852 --> 00:21:44,691
That's good to hear.

194
00:21:45,251 --> 00:21:47,051
I find you're getting more handsome.

195
00:21:47,731 --> 00:21:48,504
Look at you.

196
00:21:48,504 --> 00:21:50,691
So what? You got a new girlfriend?

197
00:21:51,092 --> 00:21:53,372
Come on. I've been
with my current girlfriend.

198
00:21:54,731 --> 00:21:55,332
Hold on.

199
00:21:57,251 --> 00:21:57,852
Put it on.

200
00:21:59,771 --> 00:22:00,771
It's popular this year.

201
