210
00:22:31,132 --> 00:22:31,771
Check this out.

211
00:22:33,291 --> 00:22:34,652
This one looks perfect for you.

212
00:22:35,691 --> 00:22:36,612
- No, thanks.
- Okay.

213
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,840
Take your time. Just tell me
if you like something.

214
00:22:46,232 --> 00:22:50,744
