215
00:23:02,648 --> 00:23:04,504
(Sent; Recipient: Ren Xiaoming)

216
00:23:07,448 --> 00:23:09,048
(Recipient: Ren Xiaoming)

217
00:23:13,332 --> 00:23:15,412
(Ren Xiaoming accessed my computer.)

218
00:23:16,652 --> 00:23:20,051
(She hacked my email
and sent the video of her acting crazy.)

219
00:23:25,612 --> 00:23:27,372
(She's not sick at all.)

220
00:23:38,932 --> 00:23:39,731
Ren Xiaoming.

221
00:23:42,971 --> 00:23:45,251
Glasses are a hazard.
I'll hold onto them for you.

222
00:23:50,531 --> 00:23:52,812
There's a camera there.
Call out if anything happens.

223
00:23:53,332 --> 00:23:53,852
Okay.

224
00:23:54,172 --> 00:23:55,172
I'll wait outside.

225
00:24:24,971 --> 00:24:27,211
Alright, there is no one else.

226
00:24:28,892 --> 00:24:30,092
You don't need to act now.

227
00:24:34,251 --> 00:24:35,531
Let me tell you something.

228
00:24:36,291 --> 00:24:37,451
I checked my computer.

229
00:24:38,092 --> 00:24:40,332
I checked the email sending records.

230
00:24:44,612 --> 00:24:45,852
You sent the video.

231
00:24:46,372 --> 00:24:49,132
You. You did it.

232
00:24:50,332 --> 00:24:54,051
You sent out your private videos.

233
00:24:54,892 --> 00:24:56,572
You just wanted to tell the world

234
00:24:57,291 --> 00:25:02,051
that I'm the bad guy
who spreads his wife's private matters.

235
00:25:03,451 --> 00:25:08,291
I'm going to spread the records
of you sending these videos.

236
00:25:08,491 --> 00:25:11,132
I'm telling you,
I won't take the blame for this.

237
00:25:11,211 --> 00:25:12,451
Ever think

238
00:25:13,531 --> 00:25:15,291
you have all that evidence

239
00:25:16,892 --> 00:25:18,852
because I never really
hid anything from you?

240
00:25:21,612 --> 00:25:22,491
What are you up to?

241
00:25:25,771 --> 00:25:27,812
I know a man named Zhuo Di.

242
00:25:29,332 --> 00:25:31,211
I've met his family too.

243
00:25:48,092 --> 00:25:49,932
If this gets exposed,

244
00:25:51,412 --> 00:25:55,412
wouldn't it be much more explosive
than the news

245
00:25:56,971 --> 00:25:57,771
about a bad guy?

246
00:26:13,932 --> 00:26:14,892
You win.

247
00:26:27,932 --> 00:26:28,971
You need to do me a favor.

248
00:26:32,731 --> 00:26:33,291
What favor?

249
00:26:33,412 --> 00:26:34,132
Report me.

250
00:26:35,092 --> 00:26:35,971
Report you?

251
00:26:38,132 --> 00:26:39,731
Haven't you always said I smeared you?

252
00:26:40,971 --> 00:26:42,211
It's time for revenge.

253
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:13,170
Qidaohezi Police's
Criminal Investigation Unit.

254
00:27:14,011 --> 00:27:15,172
This is Liu Xiaoran,

255
00:27:16,412 --> 00:27:17,531
Ren Xiaoming's husband.

256
00:27:18,971 --> 00:27:19,852
I am now

257
00:27:21,652 --> 00:27:22,852
formally reporting

258
00:27:24,892 --> 00:27:28,372
that Ren Xiaoming is connected
to a homicide case.

259
00:27:29,092 --> 00:27:32,172
The evidence is in a diary.

260
00:27:33,892 --> 00:27:36,491
I have video proof
that the diary exists.

261
00:27:37,011 --> 00:27:38,691
Where is that diary now?

262
00:27:40,211 --> 00:27:42,412
I don't know. She hid it.

263
00:27:42,932 --> 00:27:43,932
Have you read that diary?

264
00:27:47,691 --> 00:27:48,531
I've read it.

265
00:27:50,451 --> 00:27:51,608
My novel

266
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:55,132
was copied from that diary.

267
00:27:58,892 --> 00:28:01,612
So who was the murderer in the diary?

268
00:28:04,850 --> 00:28:05,450
Call him back.

269
00:28:05,971 --> 00:28:06,488
Okay.

270
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,392
(Click to Shut Down)

271
00:28:10,892 --> 00:28:14,011
Sorry, the number you dialed
is powered off.

272
00:28:17,011 --> 00:28:17,572
What?

273
00:28:21,092 --> 00:28:21,812
Report it at once.

274
00:28:22,168 --> 00:28:24,932
Ren Xiaoming is a suspect
in the Qidian Middle School corpse case.

275
00:28:25,251 --> 00:28:27,211
Find out the fastest way
to get to Qingzhou.

276
00:28:27,852 --> 00:28:28,852
Shun, check the flights.

277
00:28:28,892 --> 00:28:29,852
- Okay.
- Yanzi, check the high-speed rail.

278
00:28:29,852 --> 00:28:30,424
Okay.

279
00:28:36,251 --> 00:28:39,612
Don't turn your phone on
before midnight tomorrow.

280
00:28:41,291 --> 00:28:43,812
Go to the outskirts
and find a quiet place to relax.

281
00:28:52,092 --> 00:28:53,251
You're the murderer.

282
00:28:55,771 --> 00:28:59,051
Your diary records a murder.

283
00:29:01,251 --> 00:29:02,572
But you didn't tell me.

284
00:29:04,092 --> 00:29:08,172
I even denied
the diary's existence in court.

285
00:29:11,971 --> 00:29:13,491
I perjured myself for you.

286
00:29:14,731 --> 00:29:16,011
If you hadn't copied my diary,

287
00:29:17,652 --> 00:29:19,132
we wouldn't have ended up in court.

288
00:29:21,612 --> 00:29:22,892
You said it.

289
00:29:24,932 --> 00:29:26,771
You said the diary didn't exist.

290
00:29:28,892 --> 00:29:29,771
Blame me?

291
00:29:34,132 --> 00:29:36,691
You set this trap long ago.

292
00:29:38,491 --> 00:29:41,172
You used me as a pawn
to cover up your crime.

293
00:29:42,132 --> 00:29:43,251
I even thank you

294
00:29:43,572 --> 00:29:46,491
for not presenting the diary
in court as key evidence

295
00:29:46,531 --> 00:29:47,652
and letting me win the case.

296
00:29:52,251 --> 00:29:53,451
I was so foolish.

297
00:29:54,132 --> 00:29:57,691
You think too highly of yourself.
Use you as a pawn?

298
00:30:00,852 --> 00:30:02,412
I'm not that clever.

299
00:30:03,612 --> 00:30:06,011
I couldn't predict
you would copy my diary.

300
00:30:08,572 --> 00:30:10,211
You walked right into it yourself.

301
00:30:16,092 --> 00:30:16,771
Why?

302
00:30:22,332 --> 00:30:23,092
Xiaoming.

303
00:30:24,132 --> 00:30:27,852
Then why did you ask me to report you?

304
00:30:28,771 --> 00:30:29,451
First,

305
00:30:31,372 --> 00:30:33,971
only you legitimately
have the video of my diary.

306
00:30:36,332 --> 00:30:37,051
Second,

307
00:30:39,451 --> 00:30:40,892
only if you confess yourself

308
00:30:42,132 --> 00:30:46,771
will your perjury charge
get a lighter sentence.

309
00:30:47,531 --> 00:30:48,491
And also,

310
00:30:50,372 --> 00:30:51,451
only this way

311
00:30:52,771 --> 00:30:55,691
could you clearly admit to plagiarism

312
00:30:57,172 --> 00:30:59,892
out of fear of facing criminal charges.

313
00:31:03,771 --> 00:31:05,932
I told you long ago.

314
00:31:08,451 --> 00:31:12,092
The truth will come out.

315
00:31:14,691 --> 00:31:16,092
It's only a matter of time.

316
00:31:19,412 --> 00:31:20,092
Right?

317
00:31:41,652 --> 00:31:42,572
I don't know you.

318
00:31:46,892 --> 00:31:48,451
You're not Ren Xiaoming.

319
00:31:54,332 --> 00:31:55,211
I don't know you.

320
00:32:16,572 --> 00:32:17,491
- How is it?
- How is it, Shun?

321
00:32:17,971 --> 00:32:18,812
Requires a transfer.

322
00:32:19,491 --> 00:32:20,011
Yanzi.

323
00:32:20,211 --> 00:32:21,172
No direct route.

324
00:32:21,771 --> 00:32:24,092
Ma'am, driving then.
It takes six hours by car.

325
00:32:24,132 --> 00:32:26,092
Other options
would take over seven hours anyway.

326
00:32:27,852 --> 00:32:28,491
I'll drive.

327
00:32:29,332 --> 00:32:29,944
Okay.

328
00:32:31,832 --> 00:32:36,440
(Ren Xiaoming:
Copyright Case, Divorce Case)

329
00:32:37,464 --> 00:32:39,000
(Bai Shu)

330
00:32:44,011 --> 00:32:46,771
(Wait, why do I trust her so much?)

331
00:32:47,971 --> 00:32:48,531
Wait a second.

332
00:32:49,412 --> 00:32:52,451
Yanzi, Shun,
keep a close eye on Bai Shu.

333
00:32:53,251 --> 00:32:53,784
Huang.

334
00:32:54,691 --> 00:32:56,771
Notify everyone to be on 24-7 standby.

335
00:32:56,888 --> 00:32:57,451
Yes.

336
00:35:35,416 --> 00:35:37,432
(Shipping Address: 59 Licheng Street,
Qidaohezi District, La City; Name: Huang Zhiqiang)

337
00:35:56,332 --> 00:35:59,011
Hello, Huang Yue,
I just sent you a picture.

338
00:35:59,372 --> 00:36:01,252
Take a look
and help me check this person.

339
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:03,096
Okay.

340
00:36:31,932 --> 00:36:32,491
You...

341
00:36:36,852 --> 00:36:37,812
How have you been?

342
00:36:53,051 --> 00:36:53,971
I know.

343
00:36:55,571 --> 00:36:56,732
You had me back.

344
00:37:11,192 --> 00:37:12,952
(Ge Wenjun: Qidaohezi Qidian Middle School
Statue Corpse Concealment Case)

345
00:37:12,952 --> 00:37:14,040
(The Clues Surface One by One)

346
00:37:17,432 --> 00:37:19,672
(What exactly do you want?)

347
00:37:22,584 --> 00:37:24,568
(Huang Zhiqiang)

348
00:37:27,896 --> 00:37:31,160
(Jiashu: I knew it earlier)
(Come back quickly)

349
00:37:33,112 --> 00:37:34,712
(Come back quickly)

350
00:37:38,692 --> 00:37:42,212
I went back to Qidaohezi
to tail Ge Wenjun.

351
00:37:42,700 --> 00:37:43,780
She didn't know I was back.

352
00:37:44,292 --> 00:37:47,412
So I guessed the message was from you.

353
00:38:02,212 --> 00:38:05,560
When I got the first delivery call,

354
00:38:06,051 --> 00:38:08,651
I knew you were trying
to get my address.

355
00:38:12,772 --> 00:38:14,531
Sir! Delivery service.

356
00:38:14,531 --> 00:38:15,576
(Day One)
(I knew you were back.)

357
00:38:15,576 --> 00:38:16,892
- Right there.
- (But I didn't know where you were.)

358
00:38:17,011 --> 00:38:17,732
(Address Hidden for Customer Privacy)
No address.

359
00:38:18,332 --> 00:38:20,051
Isn't there a phone number?
Call and ask!

360
00:38:20,051 --> 00:38:22,011
(So I ordered food
with Huang Zhiqiang's number.)

361
00:38:22,692 --> 00:38:24,852
(Maybe the delivery guy
could get your address.)

362
00:38:24,852 --> 00:38:27,571
Hello, delivery.
One tomato and egg rice bowl...

363
00:38:29,212 --> 00:38:29,812
He hung up.

364
00:38:30,812 --> 00:38:33,451
Why? I'm on another run.
Still have deliveries. In a rush.

365
00:38:36,952 --> 00:38:37,812
(Day Two)

366
00:38:37,812 --> 00:38:38,692
Sir, delivery service.

367
00:38:39,212 --> 00:38:39,736
Coming.

368
00:38:40,216 --> 00:38:41,336
- (The next day.)
- Here it is.

369
00:38:41,772 --> 00:38:43,412
- (I used the same number.)
- What?

370
00:38:43,491 --> 00:38:44,531
Still no address.

371
00:38:44,932 --> 00:38:46,412
It says a phone number. Call and ask.

372
00:38:47,332 --> 00:38:49,651
You ordered minced eggplant over rice.

373
00:38:50,772 --> 00:38:52,372
What? Out of town?

374
00:38:52,932 --> 00:38:54,131
I can't deliver out of town.

375
00:38:54,688 --> 00:38:55,448
He is out of town.

376
00:38:55,448 --> 00:38:57,252
I'm taking another run. I'm so busy.

377
00:38:59,544 --> 00:39:00,344
(Day Three)

378
00:39:00,344 --> 00:39:01,451
- Sir, delivery service!
- (On the third day,)

379
00:39:01,491 --> 00:39:01,911
Here.

380
00:39:01,911 --> 00:39:04,091
(I ordered stewed spare ribs
over rice, your favorite.)

381
00:39:04,971 --> 00:39:06,212
How come it's him again?

382
00:39:06,412 --> 00:39:07,372
Call him!

383
00:39:12,171 --> 00:39:15,292
You ordered stewed spare ribs over rice.

384
00:39:15,451 --> 00:39:16,536
Do you still want it?

385
00:39:18,936 --> 00:39:20,571
Okay, I know that place.

386
00:39:21,531 --> 00:39:22,571
- (You finally accepted.)
- Okay.

387
00:39:22,571 --> 00:39:23,451
I'll be there soon.

388
00:39:29,651 --> 00:39:32,571
(So I followed the delivery guy
to your place.)

389
00:40:02,491 --> 00:40:03,000
Who is it?

390
00:40:03,091 --> 00:40:03,932
Hello, food delivery.

391
00:40:05,451 --> 00:40:06,692
Enjoy your meal. Goodbye.

392
00:40:12,571 --> 00:40:14,491
(Stewed spare ribs over rice.)

393
00:40:16,131 --> 00:40:16,812
Delicious.

394
00:40:22,852 --> 00:40:26,011
In this world,
besides my parents, only you know

395
00:40:27,812 --> 00:40:28,892
it's my favorite food.

396
00:40:41,011 --> 00:40:43,611
So, after Zhang Fang changed his name
to Huang Zhiqiang,

397
00:40:43,611 --> 00:40:46,171
he worked
on this construction site, right?

398
00:40:46,212 --> 00:40:46,971
Yes.

399
00:40:47,412 --> 00:40:47,971
Okay.

400
00:40:47,971 --> 00:40:49,252
Thanks for your cooperation.

401
00:40:49,292 --> 00:40:50,852
- I'll come again if needed.
- Okay.

402
00:40:50,852 --> 00:40:51,412
Thank you.

403
00:40:52,611 --> 00:40:53,332
Huang Zhiqiang.

404
00:40:57,171 --> 00:41:00,692
For these years,
you changed your name and hid.

405
00:41:02,131 --> 00:41:03,332
Was it to avoid me?

406
00:41:04,491 --> 00:41:05,372
No.

407
00:41:06,292 --> 00:41:07,611
I left you

408
00:41:09,611 --> 00:41:10,892
to stop burdening you.

409
00:41:15,332 --> 00:41:19,932
I killed someone in a crash,
became crippled, and drowned in debt.

410
00:41:22,932 --> 00:41:26,171
I don't want you
to take them on with me.

411
00:41:28,852 --> 00:41:30,171
Didn't you ever consider

412
00:41:31,932 --> 00:41:33,332
how the car accident back then

413
00:41:36,451 --> 00:41:37,732
actually happened?

414
00:41:38,451 --> 00:41:39,011
I did.

415
00:41:41,852 --> 00:41:42,772
I often think about it.

416
00:41:44,852 --> 00:41:46,171
If only I'd listened to you.

417
00:41:46,892 --> 00:41:47,772
Not driving at night.

418
00:41:50,051 --> 00:41:50,932
Not dozing off.

419
00:41:52,212 --> 00:41:53,011
It was me.

420
00:41:54,932 --> 00:41:56,372
I ruined everything.

421
00:42:04,171 --> 00:42:06,531
Not you. It was Ge Wenjun.

422
00:42:11,491 --> 00:42:14,692
Ge Wenjun orchestrated the car accident.

423
00:42:18,648 --> 00:42:21,656
(2008)

424
00:42:22,051 --> 00:42:24,892
(Did she give you pastries
to bring to me?)

425
00:42:25,732 --> 00:42:28,412
(Did she tell you
to keep the bags open in the truck?)

426
00:42:28,852 --> 00:42:29,812
(How do you know?)

427
00:42:30,292 --> 00:42:31,292
(I know her too well.)

428
00:42:32,011 --> 00:42:34,692
(The moment I saw the pastries,
I figured it out.)

429
00:42:35,971 --> 00:42:36,852
(Guess what?)

430
00:42:37,332 --> 00:42:41,131
(She put something in the flour
that made you drowsy.)

431
00:42:57,772 --> 00:42:58,812
I'm going to kill her.

432
00:43:00,131 --> 00:43:00,892
You die first.

433
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
